    <name>Yet Another SNOMED CT Browser - uk.nhs.cfh.dsp.yasb</name>

    <description>This project provides the basic browser functionality for browsing SNOMED CT. It is based on Java
        and should be platform independent.
        It contains various modules that allow for :
        1. Generating a Lucene index for SNOMED CT.
        2. An OSGI enabled Search provider service.
        3. A basic search panel functionality for searching for SNOMED CT concepts and displaying search results.
        4. Rendering a SNOMED CT concept in a tree view for display.</description>

